-----------------------------------------------------------------------

The ChuoSeiki QT-series controllers use RS232 interface or virtual Serial via the LAN connection. It requires to install the USB driver before using. You can also install the MD51_52OPTOOL to set some parameters that can not be changed in Micro-Manager (such as customized acceleration time, motor current, sensor settings, home search settings, etc.).

To download the MD5000 USB driver and software, please follow this link
[http://www.novaelec.co.jp/down/soft/md515230ds.zip]

To download the MD5000 user manual, please follow this link [http://www.novaelec.co.jp/eng/down/file/md515230de.pdf]

The MD5000 series Serial port settings are as following:
